snippet.title: Bird Line Up
snippet.description: Bird Line Up Keep track of the numbered birds and make sure they reach their home in the right order.

snippet.title: Angry Birds: Pigs Out!
snippet.description: Angry Birds: Pigs Out! Physics puzzle. Try to erase the green pigs from each level. Cut ropes and wood to get it done.

snippet.title: Fluffy Steel
snippet.description: Fluffy Steel Puzzle game. Try to eliminate all zombies and find the portal flying from shape to shape each level.

snippet.title: Birdy
snippet.description: Birdy Eat small birds and the eagle will grow, but don't get eaten by the big birds!

snippet.title: Fuzzy McFluffenstein
snippet.description: Fuzzy McFluffenstein Jump on mice to earn more time, if your time runs out, you'll explode. Combo mice to earn more time.

snippet.title: Bird Hunting
snippet.description: Bird Hunting Shoot the birds but avoid the sparrow. If you miss the other birds they shit on you...

snippet.title: Fuzzy McFluffenstein 2
snippet.description: Fuzzy McFluffenstein 2 You have 40 seconds to kill as many mice as possible.

snippet.title: Feeding Birdy
snippet.description: Feeding Birdy Eat the yellow insects to survive. Don't eat the green insects or hit the birds or you will die!

snippet.title: Fuzzy McFluffenstein 3
snippet.description: Fuzzy McFluffenstein 3 You have two minutes to kill as many mice and hamsters as you can.

snippet.title: Swine Flu: Hamdemic
snippet.description: Swine Flu: Hamdemic Throw the pigs as far as you can over the Mexican border and finish them off with a shotgun.
